---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Basic Flow          |     If the Customer is a new user, then he will register himself   first and then login.     
                                If the Customer has already registered to the system, then he   will login.     
                                He will search for the food items he wants.     
                                He will add those food items to the cart.    
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Alternate Flow      |     Customer is not able to search for food item     
                                Customer is not able to search for specific cuisine     
                                Customer searches some irrelevant option                                                                                                                     
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Exceptional Flow    |     Forgot password, Forgot username                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Assumptions         |     Customer have basic knowledge of computer and English                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Constraints         |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Dependencies        |     Customer should know how to browse the options                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
|     Input & Output      |     Input-> Customer can search whichever product they want and   press add to cart     
                                Output-> The particular product will be added to the cart.         
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Business Rule       |     Customer can add multiple products to the cart.           
